{"tid":2172303,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆尋晚腦出血中風，醫生話抽唔到血塊出黎，咁可以點做","createTime":"2020-08-24T13:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T08:58:08.000Z","uid":290081,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbe1934d6f1ce13901c621cf6c9685839e753fd","tid":2172303,"uid":290081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"老豆尋晚突然暈左，送左去QE,照完一大輪去到今朝先推入手術室，做完手術出黎醫生話植入左2條管監察腦壓，同引流啲腦液出黎，話抽唔到腦部積血。咁依家我仲可以做啲咩老豆?搬左出黎住後少見左，對上一次同佢講野傾計已經係上個月，我真係好想佢快啲醒返，有無人知邊間醫院醫出血腦中風好啲，我就黎崩潰了😭"},{"pid":"b110e732bb340d44fbc62faa072e4e404acbac30","tid":2172303,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:33:14.000Z","msg":"天命"},{"pid":"3e0be1294697c5971a5e7a3efda2beff28ed8ea1","tid":2172303,"uid":332538,"like":9,"dislike":67,"score":-58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:36:26.000Z","msg":"爸爸有無樓？有無寫遺囑？"},{"pid":"d097c6077628f32e9ec2bc6f7e24d07f8529f30e","tid":2172303,"uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"有資產就叫佢寫定遺囑囉"},{"pid":"90bde65e1f5fbdc4aebe061c7211f59943329c85","tid":2172303,"uid":72283,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"其實如果清唔到 都係控制血壓<br />\n遲早都係個一條路<br />\n因為佢壓住中間腦干<br />\n之後拜拜"},{"pid":"0a4c76d9901abd7ed9670351b88edc02edc130a0","tid":2172303,"uid":236079,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"針灸，中藥"},{"pid":"c906d38e3fa3198887fa815d8d6f116dc262e380","tid":2172303,"uid":63670,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:43:40.000Z","msg":"針灸<br />\n普通針/電針<br />\n都有幫助<br />\n對中風之類特別好"},{"pid":"aaf93f40bf4646f80e585b4e69d7506e8d5108bf","tid":2172303,"uid":161781,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:44:33.000Z","msg":"過來人<br />\n果時醫生話攞唔翻出嚟基本上無野做到<br />\n祝福樓主老豆"},{"pid":"f1bbe09c5811719624008bd4642b48265fb790e7","tid":2172303,"uid":357665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor